        public Path getTemporaryWorkingDirectory()

        Returns:
        the Path to the generation contents.

      • aggregate

        public void aggregate(GenerationReportTo report)
        Aggregates all properties of the given report within this report. The temporaryWorkingDirectory will be overwritten on every aggregation by the passed instance's value iff not null. getTemporaryWorkingDirectory() will not be aggregated, just the first non null value will be preserved.
        Parameters:
        report - GenerationReportTo to be aggregated
